@yswdqz Do you enable the handler?

```yaml
receiver-otel:
  selector: ${SW_OTEL_RECEIVER:default}
  default:
    enabledHandlers: ${SW_OTEL_RECEIVER_ENABLED_HANDLERS:"oc,otlp"}
```

@kezhenxu94 Should we enable both in default? I noticed you use System env to override `oc` by `otlp` in your PR. Could we have both? I think it is much easier. Further, should we merge `enabledOcRules` and ` enabledOtlpRules`?
